::Stasis Pod::

::A stasis pod, wandering around earth aimlessly for some time, scanned the 
planet earth.  It's corridinates were lost, so it stayed suspended in earth's 
orbit.  It was still in the deep blackness of outside space, but slowly 
making its way down to the small blue planet.::
